WEBVTT

01:53.800 --> 01:54.800
All right.

01:56.479 --> 01:57.640
Keep it a secret.

01:58.720 --> 02:00.200
Don't let the kid know.

02:17.720 --> 02:18.520
What's wrong?

02:23.120 --> 02:23.920
What's wrong?

02:24.520 --> 02:25.120
Well,

02:25.200 --> 02:28.079
the teacher asked me to buy an English dictation tape,

02:28.079 --> 02:29.210
and I'm out of money.

02:29.840 --> 02:30.900
I'll get it for you.

02:34.800 --> 02:36.760
Mom, what's wrong?

02:37.000 --> 02:37.860
Are you crying?

02:38.960 --> 02:40.920
I just put in some eye drops.

02:40.960 --> 02:42.200
I don't know what's wrong today.

02:42.200 --> 02:43.200
My eyes

02:43.640 --> 02:45.300
keep feeling uncomfortable.

02:46.600 --> 02:47.720
Here, take it all.

02:48.360 --> 02:49.440
This is so much.

02:49.520 --> 02:50.250
Is it enough?

02:50.440 --> 02:51.560
Of course it's enough.

02:51.560 --> 02:52.820
Go to sleep early, son.

02:53.720 --> 02:54.520
Got it, Mom.

02:55.240 --> 02:56.120
Go to sleep.

02:56.160 --> 02:56.890
Thanks, Dad.

03:09.800 --> 03:10.800
The drama performance.

03:10.800 --> 03:12.730
Don't you want to show your talent?

03:14.640 --> 03:15.600
From now until the summer vacation,

03:15.600 --> 03:17.560
there is a city track and field selection competition.

03:17.560 --> 03:19.079
I have to leave to prepare for a while,

03:19.079 --> 03:20.410
so I won't participate.

03:21.640 --> 03:23.880
You are participating for Yuanbao, right?

03:23.880 --> 03:25.340
What role are you playing?

03:27.280 --> 03:29.560
I guess she must be Zixia.

03:30.079 --> 03:31.600
So I have to play Joker.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.720
The secret I told you,

03:34.880 --> 03:35.940
you can't tell her.

03:36.160 --> 03:37.040
Don't worry.

03:38.400 --> 03:39.040
By the way,

03:39.280 --> 03:40.680
about our grandparents,

03:40.720 --> 03:41.680
keep an eye on it.

03:42.000 --> 03:43.360
I think it's very important.

03:43.360 --> 03:44.640
I care more than you do.

03:45.280 --> 03:47.280
But we have to work on Yuanbao first.

03:47.840 --> 03:49.400
Come on, let's compete.

03:50.600 --> 03:52.460
Showing off in front of an expert.

03:52.680 --> 03:54.280
Then, expert, are you ready?

03:54.600 --> 03:56.840
I will count to three. Listen carefully.

03:56.840 --> 03:58.079
Ready... Three!

03:58.840 --> 04:00.040
Why are you cheating?

04:02.640 --> 04:04.840
If heaven gave me another chance,

04:05.200 --> 04:07.200
I would say three words to that girl:

04:07.520 --> 04:08.440
"I love you."

04:08.760 --> 04:10.720
If I had to put a time limit

04:10.720 --> 04:12.240
on this love,

04:12.560 --> 04:15.000
I hope it would be 10,000 years.

04:24.400 --> 04:25.240
No, no.

04:25.960 --> 04:28.240
I'm so nervous even when I'm acting alone.

04:28.240 --> 04:30.400
What will I do when I perform on stage?

04:30.440 --> 04:32.970
What should I do? I won't even be able to speak.

04:33.840 --> 04:34.360
No, no.

04:34.680 --> 04:36.720
Xiong Yuanbao, you have to pull yourself together.

04:36.720 --> 04:39.040
I will get it together.

04:39.280 --> 04:40.640
You can do this, Xiong Yuanbao.

04:40.640 --> 04:41.920
You are the best.

04:42.080 --> 04:44.080
You are the next Oscar Best Actress.

04:49.320 --> 04:50.250
Why are you here?

04:55.159 --> 04:56.090
Have some water.

04:57.280 --> 04:57.960
Thank you.

05:04.720 --> 05:05.650
Feeling better?

05:08.040 --> 05:08.840
Much better.

05:09.440 --> 05:10.080
By the way,

05:10.800 --> 05:13.800
thank you for also recommending 'A Chinese Odyssey'.

05:14.000 --> 05:16.400
We're desk mates. It's the least I could do.

05:16.840 --> 05:17.640
Besides,

05:18.640 --> 05:19.970
I want to ask you a favor,

05:20.240 --> 05:21.640
a presumptuous request.

05:22.480 --> 05:23.320
You saved me.

05:23.720 --> 05:24.960
Tell me, what do you need?

05:24.960 --> 05:26.560
I'll help you as much as I can.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.860
I want to try for Joker.

05:29.280 --> 05:30.960
Would you act with me?

05:38.240 --> 05:39.370
Is it too much to ask?

05:40.159 --> 05:40.840
No.

05:41.000 --> 05:42.800
It's not hard. I can do it.

05:46.760 --> 05:47.600
What's this?

05:48.000 --> 05:50.040
I picked some good clips,

05:50.440 --> 05:51.880
and printed out the corresponding lines.

05:51.880 --> 05:52.680
Take a look.

05:54.320 --> 05:55.920
You are amazing.

05:58.640 --> 05:59.880
But I heard

06:00.400 --> 06:03.640
Yaqi also wants the role of Fairy Zixia.

06:04.480 --> 06:06.080
If you act with her,

06:06.160 --> 06:07.960
your chances of winning will be higher.

06:07.960 --> 06:09.440
Why did you choose me?

06:10.000 --> 06:11.130
I'm looking forward

06:12.240 --> 06:14.300
to Yuanbao's version of Fairy Zixia.

06:14.360 --> 06:16.120
If you don't play Fairy Zixia,

06:16.560 --> 06:18.920
I'm not interested in Joker either.

06:20.960 --> 06:22.020
You must work hard.

06:22.560 --> 06:23.760
I'll be watching you.

06:26.040 --> 06:28.000
Okay, I will.

06:28.720 --> 06:30.120
I know an acting teacher.

06:30.240 --> 06:31.700
Are you free after school?

06:32.000 --> 06:33.360
I'll ask her for some guidance.

06:33.360 --> 06:34.420
Let's go together.

06:35.200 --> 06:35.960
Really?

06:36.400 --> 06:37.960
Can I go with you?

06:38.080 --> 06:38.880
Of course.

06:41.240 --> 06:41.680
Okay.

06:47.400 --> 06:47.930
Yuanbao.

06:47.960 --> 06:49.159
I'm in a rush to my tutoring class.

06:49.159 --> 06:49.840
I'm leaving now.

06:49.840 --> 06:50.760
Okay, go.

06:50.800 --> 06:51.480
Okay, bye.

06:52.159 --> 06:53.280
Are you ready?

06:54.040 --> 06:54.640
Almost.

06:56.280 --> 06:58.680
Do you need to call your family to tell them?

06:59.159 --> 07:01.280
I've already texted my family.

07:01.320 --> 07:03.360
I told them I'm at school

07:03.840 --> 07:06.370
and will go back after finishing my homework.

07:06.600 --> 07:07.200
By the way,

07:07.400 --> 07:08.840
where does the teacher live?

07:08.840 --> 07:10.240
How are we getting there?

07:10.720 --> 07:11.450
It's not far.

07:11.640 --> 07:13.040
Just a ten-minute walk.

07:14.760 --> 07:15.400
Shorty,

07:15.480 --> 07:16.920
I'm taking you somewhere. Hurry up.

07:16.920 --> 07:17.760
Wait.

07:19.000 --> 07:19.640
What's wrong?

07:19.640 --> 07:22.120
I have plans with Meng Jingu today

07:22.160 --> 07:24.760
to study acting at the acting teacher's house.

07:24.840 --> 07:25.970
Go back by yourself.

07:28.640 --> 07:29.570
Acting teacher?

07:30.320 --> 07:31.180
Male or female?

07:31.360 --> 07:33.159
Don't worry, she's a woman.

07:34.000 --> 07:34.680
Yuanbao,

07:34.920 --> 07:36.960
I want to take you to a very important place.

07:36.960 --> 07:39.080
Can't we see this acting teacher later?

07:39.080 --> 07:40.480
She's usually very busy.

07:40.600 --> 07:41.840
Seeing her today

07:42.159 --> 07:43.560
was arranged in advance.

07:43.640 --> 07:45.040
If we go see her tomorrow,

07:45.080 --> 07:47.040
I can't guarantee she'll have time.

07:47.040 --> 07:47.840
And for Yuanbao and me

07:47.840 --> 07:49.840
to learn some professional knowledge,

07:49.840 --> 07:51.300
it's also very necessary.

07:51.480 --> 07:52.920
That's right, exactly.

07:55.760 --> 07:56.690
Then I'll go too.

07:57.520 --> 07:58.780
What are you going for?

07:59.520 --> 08:01.280
I'm a member of the group after all.

08:01.280 --> 08:02.400
Why can't I go?

08:03.200 --> 08:04.080
Besides,

08:04.400 --> 08:06.260
don't I have to pick a role to play?

08:06.320 --> 08:07.560
What role are you picking?

08:07.560 --> 08:08.820
None of your business.

08:08.880 --> 08:10.080
Anyway, if I don't go,

08:10.080 --> 08:11.480
Yuanbao can't go either.

08:12.640 --> 08:13.920
What's wrong with you today?

08:13.920 --> 08:15.450
Why are you acting so weird?

08:16.240 --> 08:17.920
Just go away.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.280
No, why won't you

08:20.280 --> 08:21.360
let me go with you?

08:21.720 --> 08:22.800
It's so dark out,

08:23.040 --> 08:24.720
and he's taking you to a strange place.

08:24.720 --> 08:26.050
You don't even know him.

08:26.200 --> 08:27.760
What if he has bad intentions?

08:27.760 --> 08:29.800
You'll have nowhere to cry when the time comes.

08:29.800 --> 08:31.360
Meng Jingu is my desk mate.

08:31.440 --> 08:33.159
How could he have any bad intentions?

08:33.159 --> 08:35.400
Besides, we're going to the teacher's house,

08:35.400 --> 08:37.159
not a lion's den.

08:37.320 --> 08:38.919
You make it sound so scary.

08:39.440 --> 08:41.919
Okay, I know you're worried about me.

08:42.280 --> 08:44.480
But Meng Jingu and I already made plans.

08:45.400 --> 08:46.560
You know,

08:46.720 --> 08:49.520
I really want to play the role of Fairy Zixia well.

08:50.080 --> 08:50.960
Don't worry.

08:51.320 --> 08:52.800
Let's go.

09:11.360 --> 09:13.490
What should I do? I'm a little nervous.

09:33.520 --> 09:35.320
Make sure to review

09:35.360 --> 09:36.600
the lesson the teacher taught today.

09:36.600 --> 09:37.320
Okay.

09:59.920 --> 10:01.200
We're almost at your house.

10:01.200 --> 10:02.600
Yeah, it's just up ahead.

10:04.040 --> 10:06.440
I heard you and Mu Qingyun are neighbors

10:06.800 --> 10:08.000
and grew up together.

10:08.360 --> 10:09.160
That's right.

10:09.360 --> 10:12.440
Our parents were classmates since they were young.

10:12.720 --> 10:14.850
Later, they worked in the same factory

10:15.040 --> 10:17.560
and lived in the same family dormitory.

10:18.080 --> 10:20.560
We were even born in the same hospital.

10:20.920 --> 10:22.380
Isn't that a coincidence?

10:22.880 --> 10:24.680
Then you must know him very well.

10:24.680 --> 10:25.560
More than that.

10:25.760 --> 10:27.420
I even know when he wet the bed.

10:29.960 --> 10:31.360
I mean,

10:31.760 --> 10:33.560
we grew up together.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.600
Have his grades

10:37.320 --> 10:38.580
always been like this?

10:39.880 --> 10:42.680
His grades were okay in elementary school.

10:43.080 --> 10:45.800
Later, he just let himself go,

10:46.000 --> 10:47.560
and his grades plummeted.

10:48.760 --> 10:49.600
I know

10:50.080 --> 10:52.160
good students like you

10:52.520 --> 10:54.840
don't really like students like Mutou.

10:55.480 --> 10:57.680
But Mutou is actually a really good guy.

10:57.920 --> 10:59.600
Besides his poor grades,

10:59.760 --> 11:01.420
he has a lot of good qualities.

11:02.120 --> 11:03.450
Has he never lied to you?

11:03.640 --> 11:04.760
Lied to me?

11:05.800 --> 11:08.060
If he dared to lie to me, he'd be dead meat.

11:08.280 --> 11:09.680
He swore an oath to me.

11:10.200 --> 11:12.000
What's wrong? Has he lied to you?

11:13.640 --> 11:15.440
Nothing. Just making conversation.

11:15.440 --> 11:16.200
Let's go.

11:25.680 --> 11:27.200
Ms. Li is quite humorous.

11:27.840 --> 11:29.240
She is very professional.

11:29.240 --> 11:30.570
Have you learned it all?

11:31.040 --> 11:32.600
I wrote it all down in my notebook.

11:32.600 --> 11:33.480
Don't worry.

11:34.080 --> 11:36.480
Let's find some time to run lines tomorrow.

11:39.000 --> 11:39.680
Mutou,

11:40.160 --> 11:41.490
what are you doing here?

11:42.760 --> 11:45.820
The weather is nice today. I came out for some fresh air.

11:51.360 --> 11:52.600
Why are you just getting back?

11:52.600 --> 11:54.960
Yuanbao and I rehearsed at the teacher's house for a while,

11:54.960 --> 11:56.160
so we were delayed.

11:56.360 --> 11:57.290
But with me here,

11:57.320 --> 11:59.520
you don't have to worry about her safety.

11:59.520 --> 12:01.640
I'm only worried because you're here.

12:01.640 --> 12:03.170
What are you talking about?

12:04.080 --> 12:04.680
Deskmate.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.880
Thanks for taking me to see the teacher today

12:06.880 --> 12:08.000
and walking me back.

12:08.000 --> 12:08.920
It's getting late.

12:08.920 --> 12:09.960
Go back and get some rest.

12:09.960 --> 12:11.760
Okay, I'll head back now.

12:13.120 --> 12:14.080
Goodbye, Zixia.

12:14.640 --> 12:15.840
Goodnight, Joker.

12:18.200 --> 12:19.000
Bye-bye.

12:22.280 --> 12:24.140
What are you doing? Let's go home.

12:25.600 --> 12:27.330
What did that guy mean just now?

12:27.600 --> 12:29.200
What Zixia and Joker?

12:29.640 --> 12:30.480
Are you two...

12:31.040 --> 12:33.200
I know this decision is a bit sudden.

12:33.240 --> 12:34.720
I haven't had time to tell you.

12:34.720 --> 12:36.380
Meng Jingu and I discussed it,

12:36.400 --> 12:38.000
and we plan to act together

12:38.040 --> 12:40.600
to try for the roles of Zixia and Joker.

12:41.360 --> 12:43.220
Why didn't you tell me in advance?

12:43.600 --> 12:45.280
I know that since we were little,

12:45.280 --> 12:47.360
I've always participated in these activities with you.

12:47.360 --> 12:49.440
But haven't you always disliked them?

12:49.440 --> 12:50.440
I thought

12:51.000 --> 12:52.260
I shouldn't force you.

12:53.440 --> 12:54.600
This is a good thing too.

12:54.600 --> 12:56.880
If you didn't want to be with me, just say so.

12:56.880 --> 12:59.120
When did I ever say I was forcing myself to accompany you?

12:59.120 --> 13:00.400
Why have you changed?

13:00.760 --> 13:02.160
Didn't you use to dislike

13:02.160 --> 13:03.240
participating in these kinds of activities

13:03.240 --> 13:04.770
and think they were stupid?

13:04.960 --> 13:07.800
Besides, Meng Jingu is a top student.

13:07.880 --> 13:09.440
If I can act with him,

13:09.800 --> 13:12.260
won't my chances of playing Zixia be better?

13:13.520 --> 13:14.600
Why do you think

13:14.680 --> 13:16.280
he will definitely be Joker?

13:17.680 --> 13:20.440
Let me tell you, the competition hasn't started yet.

13:20.440 --> 13:22.370
It's still uncertain who will win.

13:22.400 --> 13:24.120
If he doesn't get selected as Joker...

13:24.120 --> 13:25.650
Don't be too disappointed.

13:26.400 --> 13:28.240
What do you mean it's up for grabs?

13:28.240 --> 13:29.970
Mutou, are you participating?

13:30.560 --> 13:31.520
Wait for me.

13:34.480 --> 13:37.160
It's just memorizing lines to compete for Zhi Zun Bao.

13:37.160 --> 13:38.220
Anyone can do that.

13:38.400 --> 13:39.400
I'll show you

13:39.520 --> 13:42.360
who the real Zhi Zun Bao is.

13:45.040 --> 13:46.240
You should do this.

13:47.240 --> 13:48.720
I deserve to die too.

13:50.000 --> 13:51.920
Once, there was a sincere love.

14:27.080 --> 14:28.040
Stop.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.320
Bro, why did you just

14:54.320 --> 14:56.450
shout 'shut up' during the open class?

15:01.400 --> 15:04.530
Don't bring it up. It makes me mad just thinking about it.

15:10.200 --> 15:10.800
You two,

15:10.840 --> 15:13.000
um, I'll be taking my leave now.

15:18.680 --> 15:20.140
Mind having a chat with me?

15:22.720 --> 15:23.850
It's about Yuanbao.

15:24.520 --> 15:26.050
Don't you want to talk to me?

15:28.560 --> 15:29.820
What do you want to say?

15:31.000 --> 15:32.200
It seems only matters regarding Yuanbao

15:32.200 --> 15:33.400
can make you care.

15:33.840 --> 15:35.960
Cut the crap. Just say it.

15:36.200 --> 15:36.680
But right now,

15:36.680 --> 15:39.480
I suddenly don't want to talk about Yuanbao anymore.

15:39.480 --> 15:41.600
Are you tricking me?

15:42.840 --> 15:45.200
Forget it. I'll just be straightforward.

15:51.960 --> 15:53.420
'A Brief History of Time.'

15:53.720 --> 15:55.320
I still recognize these words.

15:55.320 --> 15:56.320
Stop pretending.

15:57.400 --> 15:59.160
You are clearly a physics genius.

15:59.160 --> 16:00.080
Why did you pretend to know nothing

16:00.080 --> 16:01.160
in the class?

16:01.960 --> 16:02.880
You didn't cheat on the physics test.

16:02.880 --> 16:03.960
Why did you admit it

16:04.040 --> 16:05.370
and say you copied mine?

16:05.680 --> 16:06.610
What do you mean?

16:06.800 --> 16:07.860
Why did you do that?

16:08.760 --> 16:09.520
I know.

16:09.960 --> 16:11.600
You are Alpha.

16:19.160 --> 16:21.640
No wonder. He is Gamma.

16:22.560 --> 16:24.600
It's a small world.

16:25.720 --> 16:28.160
Fine. Since you've brought it up,

16:28.800 --> 16:31.000
there's no need for me to hide it anymore.

16:31.000 --> 16:32.440
I can tell you,

16:33.000 --> 16:35.060
but you must swear to keep it a secret.

16:44.560 --> 16:45.360
Actually,

16:46.160 --> 16:47.400
Yuanbao and I

16:48.200 --> 16:49.680
are not from around here.

16:50.800 --> 16:52.080
Not from around here?

16:57.440 --> 16:58.360
Yuanbao and I

16:59.120 --> 17:00.440
are actually from the distant

17:00.440 --> 17:01.800
Blablabla Planet.

17:02.720 --> 17:04.640
Our planet was attacked

17:04.640 --> 17:06.599
by Hulahulahula aliens.

17:07.160 --> 17:08.319
I, as a prince,

17:08.520 --> 17:09.780
and she, as a princess,

17:10.079 --> 17:11.960
arrived on Earth

17:12.160 --> 17:14.690
under the desperate escort of our ministers.

17:14.800 --> 17:16.460
The ministers who escorted us

17:17.160 --> 17:18.819
also sacrificed themselves.

17:19.440 --> 17:22.200
We are the only survivors

17:22.240 --> 17:23.599
of Blablabla Planet.

17:24.319 --> 17:26.849
So we have to desperately hide our identities

17:27.319 --> 17:28.480
to survive.

17:29.800 --> 17:31.400
Do people from Blabla Planet

17:31.440 --> 17:32.770
also like to drink coke?

17:35.160 --> 17:36.160
We have no choice.

17:37.120 --> 17:38.240
We have to survive.

17:38.760 --> 17:39.480
Also,

17:39.600 --> 17:41.200
we are not from Blabla Planet,

17:41.200 --> 17:42.720
but Blablabla.

17:43.080 --> 17:44.410
I haven't finished yet.

17:44.800 --> 17:46.800
Our planet has explicit rules

17:46.920 --> 17:48.880
that we can't get too close to Earthlings.

17:48.880 --> 17:50.400
Yuanbao has a special constitution.

17:50.400 --> 17:51.800
If she interacts with you Earthlings,

17:51.800 --> 17:53.280
especially men like you,

17:53.400 --> 17:55.080
and has too much physical contact,

17:55.080 --> 17:56.810
it will shorten your lifespan.

17:56.840 --> 17:57.680
I'm not trying to scare you.

17:57.680 --> 17:58.760
Do you understand?

18:01.200 --> 18:03.660
Aren't you being punished to stand? Go back.

18:04.800 --> 18:06.200
I'm telling you a secret.

18:06.240 --> 18:08.400
I'm only saying this because I see you as a bro.

18:08.400 --> 18:09.760
You beat around the bush

18:10.520 --> 18:13.180
just to stop me from acting with Yuanbao, right?

18:13.480 --> 18:14.280
No.

18:15.400 --> 18:16.840
Of course, if you don't want

18:16.840 --> 18:18.360
your internal organs to be jinxed by her

18:18.360 --> 18:19.360
and burst!

18:20.000 --> 18:20.480
That would be so tragic.

18:20.480 --> 18:22.140
You'd better drop it, really.

18:23.840 --> 18:25.040
I'm the kind of person

18:25.440 --> 18:27.370
who has a really strong curiosity.

18:27.720 --> 18:28.680
I'm also

18:28.840 --> 18:29.900
very competitive.

18:30.400 --> 18:31.800
Since you put it that way,

18:31.960 --> 18:34.000
I simply must act with Yuanbao.

18:34.240 --> 18:35.280
I'll see if

18:35.360 --> 18:37.840
my internal organs will go pfft-pfft.

18:42.840 --> 18:44.080
Then you're dead.

18:45.280 --> 18:48.520
Your internal organs will go pfft-pfft sooner or later.

18:51.360 --> 18:54.200
Someone told a huge lie

18:54.280 --> 18:55.480
and fooled everyone,

18:55.920 --> 18:57.050
including Yuanbao.

18:59.040 --> 19:00.440
When your lie is exposed,

19:01.040 --> 19:02.400
will your internal organs

19:02.400 --> 19:04.000
be the ones going pfft-pfft?

19:08.720 --> 19:11.000
Alpha, don't forget,

19:11.600 --> 19:13.130
you still owe me a question.

19:13.880 --> 19:14.920
So from now on,

19:15.040 --> 19:16.900
including the role of Zhi Zun Bao,

19:16.960 --> 19:18.240
I won't lose to you.

19:25.200 --> 19:26.680
I didn't expect

19:27.200 --> 19:28.760
that he is Gamma.

19:29.040 --> 19:31.960
Was this guy a fighting cock in his past life?

19:34.960 --> 19:35.720
He

19:36.040 --> 19:38.160
won't tell Yuanbao my secret, right?

19:46.520 --> 19:47.280
Ning Yu,

19:47.760 --> 19:48.840
leave it to me.

19:54.160 --> 19:54.690
Oh my god.

19:54.720 --> 19:55.640
Class Monitor.

19:56.160 --> 19:57.020
Class Monitor.

19:57.960 --> 19:58.960
I'm sorry, Class Monitor.

19:58.960 --> 19:59.640
Are you okay?

19:59.640 --> 20:00.360
I didn't mean it.

20:00.360 --> 20:01.120
Are you okay?

20:01.400 --> 20:02.200
I'm fine.

20:03.720 --> 20:05.720
It's all red, how can you be fine?

20:06.000 --> 20:07.240
Well, I'll take you to the infirmary.

20:07.240 --> 20:08.500
You guys keep playing.

20:08.720 --> 20:09.850
Let's go take a look.

20:09.920 --> 20:10.560
Let's go.

20:13.960 --> 20:15.040
I'm sorry.

20:18.840 --> 20:19.560
Qingyun,

20:19.840 --> 20:22.200
thank you for taking me to the Western Pharmacy.

20:22.200 --> 20:23.760
I'm actually fine.

20:24.640 --> 20:25.800
I'm really sorry.

20:26.200 --> 20:27.600
We didn't mean to

20:28.520 --> 20:29.850
hit your head like that.

20:30.120 --> 20:32.520
If it still hurts, remember to come find us.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.960
Yuanbao is so serious recently.

20:38.120 --> 20:41.000
I heard she's going to act with Meng Jingu.

20:42.520 --> 20:46.600
If I also want to fight for the role of Zixia Fairy,

20:47.200 --> 20:49.160
are you willing to act with me?

20:52.600 --> 20:53.400
It's okay.

20:53.600 --> 20:54.280
I know

20:54.480 --> 20:56.520
you have such a good relationship with Yuanbao.

20:56.520 --> 20:57.520
I can understand.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.120
Alright.

21:09.680 --> 21:10.600
I promise you.

21:11.240 --> 21:13.400
You play Zixia, and I'll play Zhizunbao.

21:13.400 --> 21:14.640
Is that really okay?

21:19.080 --> 21:20.280
Why not?

21:20.560 --> 21:21.620
As long as I'm here,

21:21.720 --> 21:23.580
we will definitely win the roles.

21:34.360 --> 21:35.600
What about Yuanbao?

21:48.680 --> 21:49.400
Yuanbao,

21:50.680 --> 21:51.440
are you okay?

21:52.840 --> 21:53.480
I'm fine.

21:54.040 --> 21:55.240
Let's run the lines.

21:56.520 --> 21:57.850
We will definitely win.

22:01.360 --> 22:02.000
Come on.

22:06.840 --> 22:07.840
Why do you want to act

22:07.840 --> 22:09.680
with the class monitor today?

22:11.920 --> 22:13.480
What? You wanna control me?

22:13.800 --> 22:14.920
No, I don't.

22:15.840 --> 22:17.320
But then again,

22:17.600 --> 22:18.840
did you force yourself to choose Joker

22:18.840 --> 22:20.500
just because you wanted to act

22:20.640 --> 22:22.520
with the class monitor?

22:23.200 --> 22:24.660
I'm kindly reminding you.

22:24.920 --> 22:26.850
If you really want to participate,

22:26.920 --> 22:28.920
I advise you to choose another role.

22:29.200 --> 22:31.730
I'm afraid you can't compete with Meng Jingu.

22:32.720 --> 22:34.600
I just don't understand

22:34.840 --> 22:36.800
what's so good about Meng Jingu

22:36.960 --> 22:38.600
that makes you place such high hopes on him.

22:38.600 --> 22:39.720
You don't even know

22:39.800 --> 22:41.530
what this guy has up his sleeve.

22:41.680 --> 22:43.160
He might ditch you halfway

22:43.240 --> 22:44.770
to act with someone better.

22:47.360 --> 22:48.760
What are you laughing at?

22:48.920 --> 22:50.800
Meng Jingu is excellent in character and learning.

22:50.800 --> 22:51.730
He's a gentleman

22:52.080 --> 22:54.120
who always keeps his promises.

22:54.320 --> 22:56.120
I'm just trying to make progress

22:56.360 --> 22:58.360
by acting with the top student in our grade.

22:58.360 --> 22:59.360
This way,

22:59.480 --> 23:01.600
my grades will improve faster.

23:01.920 --> 23:02.600
Fine.

23:02.800 --> 23:04.440
The midterms are coming up.

23:05.000 --> 23:07.360
I'd like to see if your grades can improve.

23:08.480 --> 23:11.040
With his all-around development,

23:11.240 --> 23:13.480
it'll be convenient to ask him questions I don't know.

23:13.480 --> 23:14.280
Besides,

23:14.480 --> 23:17.140
I've always been working harder than you, okay?

23:23.960 --> 23:25.160
Let's read it when we get home.

23:25.160 --> 23:25.880
I'm hungry.

23:34.280 --> 23:35.960
Better to rely on yourself.

23:36.000 --> 23:36.730
Some say that

23:36.760 --> 23:37.960
every high school student

23:37.960 --> 23:39.640
is like a lonely warrior,

23:40.000 --> 23:41.330
fighting alone in every

23:41.360 --> 23:43.000
cold late night.

23:43.440 --> 23:44.800
Those sets of test papers

23:44.800 --> 23:46.400
and workbooks

23:46.480 --> 23:48.760
are the stepping stones to our dreams.

23:49.000 --> 23:51.480
We just have to keep working hard.

23:51.640 --> 23:53.920
Only then can we stand higher and see further,

23:53.920 --> 23:56.520
and witness scenery we have never seen before.

23:56.600 --> 23:57.440
Zixia,

23:57.520 --> 23:58.680
I will work hard too.

24:27.120 --> 24:27.360
Chemistry...

24:27.360 --> 24:27.600
Chem... Mr. Xu.

24:27.600 --> 24:28.600
Um, Mr. Xu.

24:29.080 --> 24:29.920
Outside of work,

24:29.920 --> 24:31.200
what are your hobbies?

24:31.520 --> 24:32.800
I like working out,

24:32.840 --> 24:33.400
and

24:33.440 --> 24:35.570
occasionally enjoy watching movies.

24:41.200 --> 24:43.000
"Call for Love".

24:44.280 --> 24:46.010
"Love Cannot be Transferred".

24:47.560 --> 24:49.000
"Secret".

24:49.680 --> 24:50.610
This one is good.

24:55.560 --> 24:56.160
Hello.

24:56.320 --> 24:58.120
I want two tickets for 'Secret'.

25:50.640 --> 25:52.000
Grandma, I'm back.

25:52.840 --> 25:54.040
Yuanbao is back.

25:56.040 --> 25:57.440
Wash your hands quickly.

25:57.560 --> 26:00.290
We're going to Qingyun's house for dinner later.

26:01.200 --> 26:02.600
How did you do on the exam?

26:04.040 --> 26:05.080
Not bad.

26:06.240 --> 26:09.080
You have to study hard.

26:09.600 --> 26:10.240
All right.

26:10.240 --> 26:11.440
I got it.

26:14.400 --> 26:15.480
My stomach hurts.

26:15.720 --> 26:16.880
I'm going to the bathroom.

26:16.880 --> 26:18.000
Wait, did you

26:18.240 --> 26:19.120
eat something bad

26:19.120 --> 26:20.720
outside again?

26:24.760 --> 26:25.890
By the way, Grandma.

26:25.920 --> 26:28.520
We're having a parent-teacher meeting tomorrow.

26:28.520 --> 26:29.160
I know.

26:29.320 --> 26:30.720
Your aunt will go for you,

26:30.800 --> 26:32.520
and Mr. Mu will go for Qingyun.

26:32.880 --> 26:34.680
Hasn't it always been like this?

26:35.360 --> 26:36.080
I got it.

26:43.280 --> 26:44.240
This child.

26:45.640 --> 26:47.920
She must really want her parents

26:48.160 --> 26:50.360
to attend her parent-teacher meeting.

26:51.960 --> 26:53.640
Son, this time,

26:53.720 --> 26:55.080
you did well on your exam.

26:55.080 --> 26:56.200
Your teacher, Mr. Tian,

26:56.200 --> 26:57.600
is full of praise for you.

26:57.800 --> 26:58.930
Mom is very pleased.

27:00.720 --> 27:01.560
Brat.

27:02.040 --> 27:03.760
Here, take this.

27:04.560 --> 27:05.760
This is your reward.

27:06.160 --> 27:07.160
You did a good job.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.520
Don't you like sneakers?

27:09.800 --> 27:11.060
Go buy them if you like.

27:11.200 --> 27:12.760
As long as you get good grades,

27:12.760 --> 27:14.290
Dad will give you anything.

27:16.080 --> 27:17.760
Son, take it.

27:18.560 --> 27:20.620
You did an excellent job on this exam.

27:20.920 --> 27:22.280
Your dad is very happy.

27:22.760 --> 27:24.490
Keep up the good work next time.

27:24.760 --> 27:25.680
I don't need it.

27:26.560 --> 27:28.290
Isn't first place all you want?

27:28.560 --> 27:30.560
Isn't it enough that I gave it to you?

27:30.600 --> 27:31.760
What are you saying?

27:33.520 --> 27:35.320
You don't want the money, right?

27:37.320 --> 27:38.780
Is having money a big deal?

27:42.200 --> 27:43.160
This brat,

27:43.600 --> 27:45.060
how dare he talk back to me.

27:45.160 --> 27:45.960
All right.

27:46.040 --> 27:47.320
You have a bad heart.

27:57.200 --> 27:58.080
Ruirui, this...

27:58.080 --> 27:58.800
Shang Ningyu,

27:58.800 --> 27:59.720
what a coincidence.

27:59.720 --> 28:00.800
What are you doing so late?

28:00.800 --> 28:02.060
I just finished class.

28:02.280 --> 28:03.840
You're out so late...

28:03.960 --> 28:06.000
I... I'm exercising.

28:06.440 --> 28:07.970
You brat! Stop right there!

28:08.560 --> 28:09.600
Ruirui, I have to go.

28:09.600 --> 28:10.280
Gotta run for my life!

28:10.280 --> 28:12.600
You got a low score again and made me sit in the special seat!

28:12.600 --> 28:14.160
Let's talk this out.

28:14.400 --> 28:15.280
Shang Ningyu.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.120
Ouch! Mom!

28:19.160 --> 28:21.880
So his mom is this tough.

28:22.640 --> 28:24.040
I'm sorry.

28:51.320 --> 28:52.240
Slippers.

28:59.360 --> 29:00.280
Leave me alone.

29:03.880 --> 29:05.340
I'll go get you some water.

29:07.880 --> 29:08.720
Qiao Yan.

29:10.960 --> 29:12.960
Are your exam results out?

29:13.600 --> 29:14.720
Show them to me.

29:36.200 --> 29:37.160
Hurry up.

29:43.960 --> 29:45.000
What happened?

29:46.440 --> 29:47.900
Your grades are dropping.

29:48.680 --> 29:49.680
Say something!

29:50.080 --> 29:51.000
Are you mute?

29:52.640 --> 29:54.760
I'll be careful next time.

29:59.320 --> 30:00.000
You...

30:00.280 --> 30:02.610
You're getting more and more ridiculous.

30:06.080 --> 30:07.040
Speak!

30:08.240 --> 30:09.080
Are you mute?

30:31.320 --> 30:32.520
Ms. Xu, well...

30:32.560 --> 30:33.680
This weekend, I...

30:34.680 --> 30:36.410
I want to invite you to watch...

30:37.200 --> 30:38.200
Well, we...

30:42.720 --> 30:44.980
Dropping the ball at the crucial moment.

30:59.040 --> 31:01.720
See you at the cinema this weekend.

31:02.360 --> 31:03.560
Be there or be square.

31:03.840 --> 31:06.520
Someone who has admired you for a long time.

31:10.120 --> 31:11.840
Subtle but elegant.

31:12.480 --> 31:14.410
And has a certain sense of mystery.

31:15.360 --> 31:16.360
Awesome!

31:31.400 --> 31:33.200
Well, Ms. Xu.

31:33.840 --> 31:35.040
See you this weekend.

31:36.480 --> 31:38.440
My heart is beating so fast.

31:40.000 --> 31:42.240
My Mr. Right is nearby.

31:46.040 --> 31:48.000
Qingyun, it's your turn.

31:50.480 --> 31:51.480
To where?

31:52.480 --> 31:53.600
Are you tired?

31:53.840 --> 31:55.480
Shall we take a break?

31:56.400 --> 31:57.200
No.

31:57.960 --> 32:00.000
Hearing you say your lines

32:00.320 --> 32:01.650
made me more confident.

32:01.720 --> 32:04.050
We will definitely win the championship.

32:06.080 --> 32:07.410
I've watched this movie

32:07.560 --> 32:09.480
almost eighty-one times.

32:11.360 --> 32:14.090
By the way, Yuanbao has been working hard lately.

32:14.200 --> 32:16.200
I saw her go to the roof just now.

32:16.480 --> 32:18.610
She seemed to be practicing lines too.

32:20.840 --> 32:21.600
The roof?

32:25.480 --> 32:27.880
Well, I'll go check on the enemy.
